Description: # naive-stopwords
        Stop words for Chinese.
        
        
        ## Installation
        
        ```bash
        pip install -U naive-stopwords
        ```
        
        ## Usage
        
        ```python
        from naive_stopwords import Stopwords
        
        sw = Stopwords()
        
        print(sw.size())
        print(sw.contains('hello'))
        
        sw.add('的')
        print(sw.size())
        print(sw.contains('的'))
        
        sw.remove('的')
        print(sw.size())
        print(sw.contains('的'))
        
        ```
        
